   "end": "0.280", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.440", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.040", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lieber Kollege Reusch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.080", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es w\u00e4re sch\u00f6n, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.320", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir jetzt nach fast zwei Stunden auch mal wieder \u00fcber etwas anderes reden k\u00f6nnten als die Befindlichkeiten der AfD-Fraktion."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.640", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Familien der Opfer des schrecklichen terroristischen Anschlags am Berliner Breitscheidplatz haben sich vor kurzem mit einem offenen Brief an die Bundeskanzlerin gewandt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.480", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Angeh\u00f6rigen machten in diesem Brief deutlich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.080", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.160", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind von den verantwortlichen Stellen und von den Regelungen zur Opferentsch\u00e4digung entt\u00e4uscht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.880", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.920", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie h\u00e4tten sich fr\u00fcher Informationen \u00fcber das Schicksal ihrer Angeh\u00f6rigen erw\u00fcnscht und diese auch erwartet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.320", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.040", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie empfinden die Regelungen zur Entsch\u00e4digung von Angeh\u00f6rigen als zu kompliziert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als zu b\u00fcrokratisch und oft auch als unzureichend. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.640", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viertens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.920", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Angeh\u00f6rigen verfolgen sehr genau, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.080", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob die Fehler der Politik und der Sicherheitsbeh\u00f6rden im Zusammenhang mit der Gefahr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.800", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die von dem Attent\u00e4ter Anis Amri schon vor dem Anschlag ausging, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.800", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier aufgearbeitet werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.720", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist das Mindeste, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.160", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir heute an dieser Stelle tun k\u00f6nnen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.520", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
