   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir eine Verantwortung f\u00fcr solche Vorf\u00e4lle tragen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.680", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine solche Kausalit\u00e4t mag im Einzelfall vorliegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.600", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist jedoch ganz offen die Frage zu formulieren: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.120", 
   "id": "s000092", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welche M\u00f6glichkeiten hat eigentlich die Politik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.960", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Sicherheit der B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger zu gew\u00e4hrleisten? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.360", 
   "id": "s000094", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da gibt es zwei Herangehensweisen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.400", 
   "id": "s000095", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.360", 
   "id": "s000096", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich im Umgang mit solchen Ereignissen von Angst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.200", 
   "id": "s000097", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von Hass, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.880", 
   "id": "s000098", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von negativen Gef\u00fchlen leiten lassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.760", 
   "id": "s000099", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es gibt diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.640", 
   "id": "s000100", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die klar und deutlich bekennen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.720", 
   "id": "s000101", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine hundertprozentige Sicherheit wird es auch mit den von Ihnen vorgeschlagenen geschlossenen Grenzen nicht geben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.040", 
   "id": "s000102", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist eine Illusion,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.600", 
   "id": "s000103", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der man redlicherweise nicht verfallen sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.880", 
   "id": "s000104", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man sicherheitspolitisch seri\u00f6s argumentieren will. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.480", 
   "id": "s000105", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen bitte ich darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.600", 
   "id": "s000106", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir bei der Sache bleiben und uns den Brief der Opferfamilien noch einmal genau zu Gem\u00fcte f\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.080", 
   "id": "s000107", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in dem sehr klar daf\u00fcr pl\u00e4diert wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "300.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.560", 
   "id": "s000108", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die H\u00f6he der Entsch\u00e4digungszahlungen massiv heraufzusetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "304.400", 
   "id": "s000109", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das unterst\u00fctzt die FDP-Fraktion gerne, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "304.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.200", 
   "id": "s000110", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber Ihre Kausalit\u00e4tsspielchen nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.440", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Neben der \u00dcberarbeitung der rechtlichen Regelung bedarf es auch einer \u00dcberarbeitung des Verfahrens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "315.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "318.480", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schauen wir uns die beiden zentralen Anspruchsgrundlagen an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "318.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.240", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist zum einen das Opferentsch\u00e4digungsgesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "326.000", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es sind zum anderen die sogenannten H\u00e4rteleistungen f\u00fcr Opfer terroristischer Straftaten aus dem Bundeshaushalt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "326.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "332.720", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In beiden Regelungsbereichen l\u00e4uft das Ganze im Falle Breitscheidplatz am Ende auf eine H\u00e4rtefallregelung hinaus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "332.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "337.360", 
   "id": "s000116", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Opferentsch\u00e4digungsgesetz ist nach seinem Wortlaut nicht anwendbar auf Angriffe mit Kraftfahrzeugen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "337.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "342.320", 
   "id": "s000117", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erst durch eine ministerielle Vereinbarung kann ein H\u00e4rtefall festgestellt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "342.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "345.480", 
   "id": "s000118", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei der Opferentsch\u00e4digung aus dem Bundeshaushalt verh\u00e4lt es sich \u00e4hnlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "345.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "347.040", 
   "id": "s000119", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schon in der Pr\u00e4ambel hei\u00dft es, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "347.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "349.680", 
   "id": "s000120", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf die entsprechende Leistung bestehe kein Rechtsanspruch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "349.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "350.120", 
   "id": "s000121", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "350.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "351.360", 
   "id": "s000122", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zweimal kein Anspruch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "351.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "352.560", 
   "id": "s000123", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zweimal H\u00e4rtefall. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "352.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "356.760", 
   "id": "s000124", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das bedeutet doppelte Ungewissheit f\u00fcr die Menschen in dem Moment gr\u00f6\u00dfter Trauer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "356.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "360.040", 
   "id": "s000125", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb muss dieses Verfahren dringend \u00fcberarbeitet werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "360.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "362.120", 
   "id": "s000126", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es sollte zum Beispiel einen zentralen Ansprechpartner geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "362.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "364.280", 
   "id": "s000127", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Au\u00dferdem sollte man nur einen Antrag f\u00fcr verschiedene Leistungen stellen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "364.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "365.280", 
   "id": "s000128", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der dann von den entsprechenden Stellen gemeinsam gepr\u00fcft wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "365.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "365.880", 
   "id": "s000129", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "365.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "371.800", 
   "id": "s000130", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auch auf Bundesebene schnellstm\u00f6glich ein Parlamentarischer Untersuchungsausschuss zum Fall Amri eingesetzt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "371.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "377.560", 
   "id": "s000131", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sehen dem Abschlussbericht des Opferbeauftragten Kurt Beck mit Freude entgegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "377.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "379.160", 
   "id": "s000132", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie mich noch einmal betonen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "379.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "383.000", 
   "id": "s000133", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen die schrecklichen Ereignisse vom Breitscheidplatz nicht r\u00fcckg\u00e4ngig machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "383.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "384.920", 
   "id": "s000134", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen aber gemeinsam daran arbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "384.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "391.440", 
   "id": "s000135", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Opfer anst\u00e4ndig behandelt werden und dass die Wahrscheinlichkeit f\u00fcr solche Taten in Zukunft sinkt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "391.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "391.720", 
   "id": "s000136", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "391.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "400.000", 
   "id": "s000137", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die Fraktion Die Linke spricht nun Dr.\u00a0Andr\u00e9 Hahn."
   ]
  }
 ]
}